&lt;p data-start=&quot;1363&quot; data-end=&quot;1521&quot;&gt;Prospect and qualify commercial opportunities such as warehouse doors, dock systems, sectional doors, access controls, rolling steel doors, and gate systems&lt;/p&gt;
